'''Kim Kötter''' (born 27 July 1982, [[Losser]], [[Overijssel]]<ref>[http://www.kimkotter.nl/ Kim Kötter] official website</ref>) is a Dutch director, model and beauty pageant titleholder. She was crowned [[Miss Universe Nederland]] 2002, and competed in the [[Miss Universe 2002]] pageant where she placed 11th in the preliminaries, missing the top 10 by one spot. She also competed in the [[Miss Europe]] 2002 pageant where she placed 3rd runner up.<ref>[http://www.dailytimes.com.pk/default.asp?page=story_30-12-2002_pg9_6 Miss Russia is Miss Europe]</ref> Kötter currently runs her own modelling agency, and is the organizer of the Miss [[Overijssel]], [[Miss Nederland]] and [[Miss Universe Germany]] beauty pageants. In  2011, Kötter competed on the Dutch version of the television show Fort Boyard.<ref>[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8VN252TdekE]</ref>

